It’s my understanding that spawning in the spawn rooms themselves prevents spawn camping, as players can’t enter them. This leaves very specific points/chokes as the only places where spawn camping can actually occur, if the defenders can push their ppl hard enough. It may actually be a non-issue. I share your concerns. I’d actually argue it could be even worse than in Conquest if one team gets all of the forward spawns (which will often be the case with the way most servers are set up now). Including good/quick spawn points for defenders is easier said than done imo.
